{"tid":1909113,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[以正視聽] 樓市準備Go Go Go","createTime":"2020-03-03T17:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T12:55:37.000Z","uid":316048,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8033998676c2ea89867785c6a09f5ecbb1e649","tid":1909113,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T17:47:12.000Z","msg":"當好多人期望呢個SARS 2.0 去番10幾年前個價，點知跌少少已經出現好多實力買家排隊等買樓既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋WARS 係香港疫情簡直係微乎其微，直至而家都係得兩個死亡個案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝香港人防疫意識令樓價更堅固<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要樓市大跌 ?  要現以下情況:<br />\n<br />\n1. 中產失業率上升至 5%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 唔係人人戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 每日確診雙位數字增長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 每2-3日出現死亡個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 全面公共交通停駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次樓價跌真係要等打仗，或者核洩漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b0168215987fdaa09ca0b84f9454fd0030d9a7","tid":1909113,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"樓市Go左未？"},{"pid":"50919a63586dee9eec204f561657e555facb8017","tid":1909113,"uid":73592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40b0168215987fdaa09ca0b84f9454fd0030d9a7","tid":1909113,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"樓市Go左未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"未，要租住等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf9bdd20ae5725f27aec8e53